Process:
step1: Add the fruit syrup & 80 ml sprite.
step2: squeeze the 1/2 lemon slice & stir.
step3: Add 200g ice & stir.
step4: Add 20 ml sprite.
Recipe 1: 12oz
-20 ml fruit syrup.
-1/2 lemon slice.
-200g ice.
-100 ml sprite.
Recipe 2 : 16oz
-30 ml fruit syrup.
-1 lemon slice.
-240g ice.
-120 ml sprite.
Recipe 3 : 22oz
-40 ml fruit syrup.
-1 lemon slice.
-300g ice + 40g ice.
-160 ml sprite.
